| comment "Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2024-4198 — Recovery Inhibition (ransomhub)"
| comment "Status: experimental | Level: high | ID: 3ac49857-80fe-50fe-9b25-33eda0294ffc"
